Class MapleSystemPM

java.lang.Object
de.hsrt.holbox.playground.MapleSystemPM
public class MapleSystemPM extends Object
This class implements a simple 4-bus system internally called the "Maple" problem now using actual models of PV and generators Especially with the use of Power Management
